
=============plugin user agent switcher===================

1. Type user agent switcher in google
2. Click add extention
3. Click tools---> Select default user agent---> select user agent switcher---> options ---->click import----->choose file useragentswitcher.xml file from yr computer(provided below as well)---->finish

This will give you more option for different devices


=======To convert from browser mode to mobile mode to inspect element for mobile browser/web app;

1. click tools----->Select Default user agent--->Mobile Devices--->devices--->apple or os--->select which platform using-----> version of simulator and browser as well